  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5741671/" class="title-link">非传媒人看完本书后有种扑向传媒的冲动</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5741671"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/miyazhai/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u38655462-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/miyazhai/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">米娅宅</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-01-15"
      class="main-meta">2013-01-15 14:38:05</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5741671_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   作为一个新闻界的局外人，我从《后台》这本书里窥见了记者工作和生活的一点衣角片段，记者们口中叙述的再平常不过的生活正是这个职业与众不同之所在。文中说记者、编辑们做新闻的三大原则是：及时、真实、有用。我心中也由此对记者有了自己的认识。我认为真正的记者心中有有一...

