              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/14613923/" class="">第8页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Enjolrad/" class=" " title="Enjolrad">Enjolrad</a>
                (我的纸里包着我的火。)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
